{"tid":131380,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"花曬漏水點算好","createTime":"2017-02-23T04:42:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-02T00:05:00.000Z","uid":30890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"85cd4d1f3dfcb6c0a337994e0c6f7197d78fceaf","tid":131380,"uid":30890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T04:42:12.000Z","msg":"各位巴打有個問題困擾左好耐希望大家可以集思廣益幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n先來新屋企係用儲水式電熱水爐，個問題就係個淋浴花灑每次一着熱水爐就會慢慢漏水，但最奇怪嘅係當熱水爐儲夠水之後就唔會再漏，唔知咁多位巴打會唔會諗到係咩原因？<br />\n<br />\nPs. 個花灑同縛住水龍頭條喉換過仍然都係有呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"482c1adf1ddc310583ed92e7dfc48894c13acafa","tid":131380,"uid":5858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T05:14:38.000Z","msg":"正常現象喎 好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c2e3d8b63708d0d3a790ff7689c086f5d306f78","tid":131380,"uid":62097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T05:17:58.000Z","msg":"水壓唔夠逼死舊膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e654efec7726a78a49cbdba4d74aceb8e6caa287","tid":131380,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T05:18:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/23/131735_6a2cbe4cff55ec19ae9fc4ba2a4f23dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F23%2F131735_6a2cbe4cff55ec19ae9fc4ba2a4f23dc.jpg&h=6314ed9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有冇落ed係條喉度"},{"pid":"a386666d0923b7a04e8b0c2789b16784fcd58340","tid":131380,"uid":44427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T05:31:30.000Z","msg":"沖涼最緊要係咩?緊係爐啦"},{"pid":"e1f692268ac071177fd6f8f9b3e72463b433a5ff","tid":131380,"uid":30890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T06:57:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/23/131735_6a2cbe4cff55ec19ae9fc4ba2a4f23dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F23%2F131735_6a2cbe4cff55ec19ae9fc4ba2a4f23dc.jpg&h=6314ed9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有冇落ed係條喉度</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打唔好意思小弟無知，想問下呢d係咩黎同可以係邊度買到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc1a281cc4a012dc3abe888c43c6758ab6e1a56a","tid":131380,"uid":30890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T06:58:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>水壓唔夠逼死舊膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打想問下係咩膠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ff0e8c77d9c5c1ae3c567ae4d4cadb3ac1768b","tid":131380,"uid":7374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T07:01:28.000Z","msg":"5金鋪"},{"pid":"80fc0806e2ada08deb35d492e8c2cff7e7de7871","tid":131380,"uid":57702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T07:44:23.000Z","msg":"儲夠水唔漏 開水先漏即係出水喉管問題<br />\n睇下出熱水或冷水開水時邊個位漏<br />\n影張相上來睇睇"},{"pid":"88b7e2f876ecea58bd0797afc29b92f70efd941d","tid":131380,"uid":8815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T07:46:23.000Z","msg":"去五金鋪買 4分膠皮/ &quot;快吧&quot; 換落接駁位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8301820df55fa11ec6dd03564ec116d3a8c3b31","tid":131380,"uid":57702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T07:47:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>各位巴打有個問題困擾左好耐希望大家可以集思廣益幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n先來新屋企係用儲水式電熱水爐，個問題就係個淋浴花灑每次一着熱水爐就會慢慢漏水，但最奇怪嘅係當熱水爐儲夠水之後就唔會再漏，唔知咁多位巴打會唔會諗到係咩原因？<br />\n<br />\nPs. 個花灑同縛住水龍頭條喉換過仍然都係有呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n換過條軟都出應該係出水條銅喉漏"},{"pid":"c243424fbcf4e708744d78446b133b0e2da16867","tid":131380,"uid":30890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:07:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>儲夠水唔漏 開水先漏即係出水喉管問題<br />\n睇下出熱水或冷水開水時邊個位漏<br />\n影張相上來睇睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打非常多謝你嘅專業意見，圖中兩個紅圈位都有漏水情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a669ca0d37b474f9903d91761b133ff87fc33b5e","tid":131380,"uid":30890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:08:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>儲夠水唔漏 開水先漏即係出水喉管問題<br />\n睇下出熱水或冷水開水時邊個位漏<br />\n影張相上來睇睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打非常多謝你嘅專業意見，圖中兩個紅圈位都有漏水情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/23/160758_e2ae6ce9c7e6687df15d0435421985c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F23%2F160758_e2ae6ce9c7e6687df15d0435421985c0.jpg&h=ef2f6d0f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e732b0ae53ed0f0a2efcb8b034b1861e04b88cd5","tid":131380,"uid":30890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:08:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>儲夠水唔漏 開水先漏即係出水喉管問題<br />\n睇下出熱水或冷水開水時邊個位漏<br />\n影張相上來睇睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打非常多謝你嘅專業意見，圖中兩個紅圈位都有漏水情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/23/160758_e2ae6ce9c7e6687df15d0435421985c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F23%2F160758_e2ae6ce9c7e6687df15d0435421985c0.jpg&h=ef2f6d0f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能我之前講得唔夠清晰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n<br />\n漏水個位係花囇頭既位置，一開水制儲熱水就會係花囇頭一滴滴咁滴水，其他位例如熱水爐博去水龍頭，水龍頭博去花囇條管個接駁位元全部都冇事"},{"pid":"a82974c3acd713d15436cde2c515314222a63ae1","tid":131380,"uid":30890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:11:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去五金鋪買 4分膠皮/ &quot;快吧&quot; 換落接駁位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打多謝你既意見，但想買問一問係咪就係上面另一位巴長張圖貼嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n同埋更換過程易唔易因為小弟完全係零家居智慧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e53ca10acfad0ce381ca0dd7f3773fdea44caa6","tid":131380,"uid":33499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:13:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>儲夠水唔漏 開水先漏即係出水喉管問題<br />\n睇下出熱水或冷水開水時邊個位漏<br />\n影張相上來睇睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打非常多謝你嘅專業意見，圖中兩個紅圈位都有漏水情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/23/160758_e2ae6ce9c7e6687df15d0435421985c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F23%2F160758_e2ae6ce9c7e6687df15d0435421985c0.jpg&h=ef2f6d0f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能我之前講得唔夠清晰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n<br />\n漏水個位係花囇頭既位置，一開水制儲熱水就會係花囇頭一滴滴咁滴水，其他位例如熱水爐博去水龍頭，水龍頭博去花囇條管個接駁位元全部都冇事</blockquote><br />\n電儲水式係正常，無水滴隨時谷爆！"},{"pid":"b065cf0bbdf29156af0009031ff457e29c30bab9","tid":131380,"uid":30890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:16:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>各位巴打有個問題困擾左好耐希望大家可以集思廣益幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n先來新屋企係用儲水式電熱水爐，個問題就係個淋浴花灑每次一着熱水爐就會慢慢漏水，但最奇怪嘅係當熱水爐儲夠水之後就唔會再漏，唔知咁多位巴打會唔會諗到係咩原因？<br />\n<br />\nPs. 個花灑同縛住水龍頭條喉換過仍然都係有呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n換過條軟都出應該係出水條銅喉漏</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n師兄咁想問一問係咪要成條銅喉換咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f6e06ea508e85a0f7327ae3c08da3a20555c86c","tid":131380,"uid":30890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:17:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>[quote]儲夠水唔漏 開水先漏即係出水喉管問題<br />\n睇下出熱水或冷水開水時邊個位漏<br />\n影張相上來睇睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打非常多謝你嘅專業意見，圖中兩個紅圈位都有漏水情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能我之前講得唔夠清晰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n<br />\n漏水個位係花囇頭既位置，一開水制儲熱水就會係花囇頭一滴滴咁滴水，其他位例如熱水爐博去水龍頭，水龍頭博去花囇條管個接駁位元全部都冇事</blockquote><br />\n電儲水式係正常，無水滴隨時谷爆！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打但我之前用左三年都冇事，係最近先發生咁既情況"},{"pid":"999529139271cc3ab6faf9e4488595f51f594a0c","tid":131380,"uid":44427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:27:53.000Z","msg":"換膠圈啦,老化咗"},{"pid":"11d1b11c505bf89f56bd95e3b40abd4ea78ce2a5","tid":131380,"uid":33499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:30:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>[quote]儲夠水唔漏 開水先漏即係出水喉管問題<br />\n睇下出熱水或冷水開水時邊個位漏<br />\n影張相上來睇睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打非常多謝你嘅專業意見，圖中兩個紅圈位都有漏水情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能我之前講得唔夠清晰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n<br />\n漏水個位係花囇頭既位置，一開水制儲熱水就會係花囇頭一滴滴咁滴水，其他位例如熱水爐博去水龍頭，水龍頭博去花囇條管個接駁位元全部都冇事</blockquote><br />\n電儲水式係正常，無水滴隨時谷爆！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打但我之前用左三年都冇事，係最近先發生咁既情況</blockquote><br />\n影熱水爐相睇下"},{"pid":"c8345aa60aab53f192f78e858509ef8ac691ff53","tid":131380,"uid":35878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:32:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好明顯係花灑頭要換</span>"},{"pid":"b167d08a649d00c1a5bce5664acdc17f56469d89","tid":131380,"uid":30890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T09:16:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>換膠圈啦,老化咗</blockquote><br />\n唔好意思小弟無知，膠圈即係邊個位？"},{"pid":"cfde045d4d7684ac30d644689ed77b9a74e9c258","tid":131380,"uid":30890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T09:19:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好明顯係花灑頭要換</span></blockquote><br />\n但係前排換咗個水龍頭都係咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33a3d75041170d151a1ddab48e70ab0362a47b84","tid":131380,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T09:21:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>換膠圈啦,老化咗</blockquote><br />\n唔好意思小弟無知，膠圈即係邊個位？</blockquote><br />\n拆開花灑頭，條喉就見到"},{"pid":"2e5afc58040fa6bdf0027bb10a0d3d27bbb83893","tid":131380,"uid":30890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T09:24:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>[quote]儲夠水唔漏 開水先漏即係出水喉管問題<br />\n睇下出熱水或冷水開水時邊個位漏<br />\n影張相上來睇睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打非常多謝你嘅專業意見，圖中兩個紅圈位都有漏水情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能我之前講得唔夠清晰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n<br />\n漏水個位係花囇頭既位置，一開水制儲熱水就會係花囇頭一滴滴咁滴水，其他位例如熱水爐博去水龍頭，水龍頭博去花囇條管個接駁位元全部都冇事</blockquote><br />\n電儲水式係正常，無水滴隨時谷爆！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打但我之前用左三年都冇事，係最近先發生咁既情況</blockquote><br />\n影熱水爐相睇下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/23/172241_6d490949a92a9e426d0dce899f3a4eff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F23%2F172241_6d490949a92a9e426d0dce899f3a4eff.jpg&h=d4db77fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話時話熱水爐出熱水嘅膠鬆咗（冇痴實囇個爐邊）會唔會都關事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}